Package: predictsr
Title: Access the PREDICTS database from the Natural History Museum, London
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Connor", "Duffin", , "connor.duffin@nhm.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fetches the PREDICTS database and relevant metadata from
  the Data Portal at the Natural History Museum. Data were collated from over
  400 existing spatial comparisons of local-scale biodiversity exposed to
  different intensities and types of anthropogenic pressures, from sites around
  the world. These data are licensed with a CC BY-NC 4.0 license.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
